msgid "2.11 (2026-03-10)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-10_02.11.00.md:3
msgid "Corrections in version requirement checks"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-10_02.11.00.md:5
msgid ""
"For projects taking advantage of "
"[`releng_require_version`](releng_tool.releng_require_version) to ensure "
"they are using compatible configurations, script utilities and more; the "
"v2.10 release revealed a flaw in the logic used to compare versions. This "
"resulted in a version `2.10` being assumed as older than versions such as "
"`2.9`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-10_02.11.00.md:11
msgid ""
"This release should correct the issue by ensuring split version parts are "
"converted into integer values before comparing."
msgstr ""
